OL,3,CITV's Lorraine Kelly to host Island
OL,4,CGames Opening Ceremony in Orkney
OL,6,FITV presenter Lorraine Kelly will team
OL,7,Fup with local BBC radio presenter
OL,8,FStewart Bain to host the Opening
OL,9,FCeremony of the Island Games in Orkney
OL,10,Flater this year.
OL,12,FLorraine, who is the Games Ambassador,
OL,13,Fwill form part of the celebration
OL,14,Fwhich will see around 2,000 athletes
OL,15,Farrive in Scotland for the 20th
OL,16,FInternational Island Games, taking
OL,17,Fplace between 12 and 18 July.
