OL,3,CITV's Lorraine Kelly to host Island
OL,4,CGames Opening Ceremony in Orkney
OL,6,FAthletes from 24 islands will go for
OL,7,Fglory in 12 sports including archery,
OL,8,Fathletics, badminton, bowls, cycling,
OL,9,Ffootball, golf, gymnastics, sailing,
OL,10,Fsquash, swimming and triathlon.
OL,12,FLorraine has described Orkney as her
OL,13,F"happy place", having been a regular
OL,14,Fvisitor to the islands for the last 40
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FShe said: "I'm so thrilled to be an
OL,18,Fambassador for Orkney 2025 and it is
OL,19,Fsuch an honour for me to have been
OL,20,Fasked to host the opening ceremony.
