OL,6,F"Orkney is a very special place to me
OL,7,Fand I've been visiting every year for
OL,8,Fthe last 40 years, so this is an
OL,9,Fincredibly exciting opportunity!
OL,11,F"I can't wait to soak up the
OL,12,Fatmosphere, from the sporting action
OL,13,Fto meeting competitors and supporters
OL,14,Ffrom the 24 islands taking part.
OL,16,F"Orkney 2025 really is a great
OL,17,Fopportunity to share with the world
OL,18,Fjust how special the islands are."
