OL,7,Fyears, with member islands taking it
OL,8,Fin turns to host the event.
OL,10,FMember islands include:
OL,12,FGuernsey hosted the Games in 2023 and
OL,13,Fattracted thousands of athletes and
OL,14,Fspectators while the 2027 Island Games
OL,15,Fwill be held in the Faroe Islands.
