OL,3,CITV's Lorraine Kelly to host Island
OL,4,CGames Opening Ceremony in Orkney
OL,6,F"The Games will not only showcase the
OL,7,Fincredible talent of island athletes
OL,8,Fbut also leave a lasting legacy for
OL,9,FOrkney. From newly developed sports
OL,10,Fclubs to improved facilities, this
OL,11,Fevent is a catalyst for growth and
OL,12,Fparticipation in sports across the
OL,13,Fislands.
OL,15,F"We are truly looking forward to
OL,16,Fseeing how this landmark occasion will
OL,17,Finspire future generations and
OL,18,Fhighlight Orkney's unique sense of
OL,19,Fcommunity and spirit."
